:title "2. Validation"
:desc /
allows to constraint document's structure and field values.

:feature-desc /
_template and _schema files.
_template is used on document creation.

_schema files are collected at startup and define document :keys.
_schema documents allows constraints on three levels:
* whole document
* a separate key
* a subdocument

^table-of [:xt/id]
:templates-defined datalog/
{:find [(pull ?e [:xt/id])]
:where [[?e :xt/id ?id]
[(clojure.string/includes? ?id "_template")]]}

^table-of [:xt/id]
:schemas-defined datalog/
{:find [(pull ?e [:xt/id])]
:where [[?e :xt/id ?id]
[(clojure.string/includes? ?id "_schema")]]}